294
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:32,280
Nonsense!

295
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,240
I don't need to explain myself to you!

296
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,080
I'll speak to Lord Lin!

297
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:34,800
Stop.

298
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,240
That is evidence.

299
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,680
Lord Lin won't give it to you.

300
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:40,480
Regardless,

301
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:42,480
it's certain that Fu Wenyuan

302
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:43,960
killed my daughter-in-law.

303
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:46,240
There's nothing wrong with me

304
00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:47,680
reclaiming her belongings!

305
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:48,800
Sooner or later,

306
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,360
you'll have to return
that pendant to me!

307
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:51,360
Hmph!

308
00:15:08,560 --> 00:15:09,280
Lu,

309
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:11,000
