310
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,160
The Evidence Room.

311
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:13,560
I have something to tell you.

312
00:15:13,920 --> 00:15:14,720
Hold on.

313
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:16,960
Let me guess

314
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,320
if we're thinking the same thing.

315
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,240
Sun Qinjiu is hiding something.

316
00:15:27,520 --> 00:15:28,920
Did you go to the Evidence Room

317
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:30,760
to find it?

318
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:32,200
Yes.

319
00:15:33,640 --> 00:15:36,080
I already found it suspicious
when Sun Qinjiu was eager

320
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:37,520
to have Fu Wenyuan executed.

321
00:15:38,280 --> 00:15:40,920
Now, he's desperately trying
to get the dowry.

322
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:42,240
I suspect

323
00:15:42,580 --> 00:15:44,400
he is actually after this jade pendant.

324
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:48,720
Jiang Mengyu's maid, Yu,

325
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:51,000
confirmed she had no affair
with Fu Wenyuan.

326
00:15:52,040 --> 00:15:53,000
But Sun Qinjiu

327
00:15:53,160 --> 00:15:54,520
insisted they did,

328
00:15:54,680 --> 00:15:56,560
using this jade pendant as the evidence.

329
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:58,520
Thinking back,

330
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:01,200
I realize he was trying
to give Fu Wenyuan

331
00:16:01,560 --> 00:16:03,160
a plausible motive for murder.

332
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:06,000
By the way,

333
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:08,040
I was just about
to go to the Evidence Room,

334
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:09,840
but you already brought what I wanted.

335
00:16:11,160 --> 00:16:12,080
We really are

336
00:16:12,400 --> 00:16:13,360
becoming more and more in sync.

337
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:29,280
I was asking

338
00:16:30,800 --> 00:16:31,960
for the pendant.

339
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:38,960
