340
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:46,560
What do you think?

341
00:16:47,400 --> 00:16:48,400
This pendant is by no means ordinary.

342
00:16:49,440 --> 00:16:51,240
It was a national treasure
of the ancient Loulan Kingdom.

343
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:52,520
Loulan Kingdom?

344
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:54,040
Yes.

345
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:56,760
This pendant is part of a pair.

346
00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:58,120
The other one is black.

347
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:01,360
This white one is made
of Tian Shan's snow jade,

348
00:17:01,920 --> 00:17:02,680
and the black one

349
00:17:03,560 --> 00:17:04,680
is made of Dragon Cave jade.

350
00:17:06,280 --> 00:17:07,200
Many years ago,

351
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:09,280
as a friendly gesture,
the Western kingdom of Loulan

352
00:17:09,840 --> 00:17:11,960
gave the black fish jade pendant
to our country.

353
00:17:12,840 --> 00:17:13,640
The late emperor

354
00:17:14,520 --> 00:17:15,920
then gave it to Grand Tutor Ji.

355
00:17:17,840 --> 00:17:18,800
Who is Grand Tutor Ji?

356
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:23,000
A corrupt official
who was later dismissed.

357
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:25,600
Then this pendant

358
00:17:26,120 --> 00:17:27,320
must be valuable.

359
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,080
It's more than valuable.

360
00:17:30,320 --> 00:17:31,600
It's priceless.

361
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:34,080
Legend has it that when the two pendants
are put together,

362
00:17:34,600 --> 00:17:36,840
a hidden treasure will be revealed,

363
00:17:37,600 --> 00:17:38,560
and the owner of this treasure

364
00:17:39,040 --> 00:17:39,640
could

365
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:42,200
change the balance of power
among nations.

366
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:44,360
Oh,

367
00:17:45,040 --> 00:17:46,600
I see.

368
00:17:47,080 --> 00:17:47,640
By the way,

369
00:17:48,080 --> 00:17:48,960
there was something else peculiar.

370
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:50,960
Yu mentioned

371
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:52,480
that on the wedding night,

372
00:17:53,160 --> 00:17:55,040
Jiang Mengyu repeatedly urged her

373
00:17:55,520 --> 00:17:58,000
to fetch Sun Ren from the banquet.

374
00:18:00,280 --> 00:18:01,800
Why did she do that?

375
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:06,080
That night,

376
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:07,760
she must have discovered something.

377
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:11,320
It seems

378
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:14,040
we need to visit the Sun Residence.

379
00:18:14,960 --> 00:18:15,600
Yes.

380
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:27,000
I haven't changed anything

381
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:28,160
in this room.

382
00:18:30,520 --> 00:18:31,920
These are Mengyu's dowry items.

383
00:18:37,240 --> 00:18:38,320
Master Sun,

384
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:40,040
do you recognize this?

385
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:47,080
But

386
00:18:48,120 --> 00:18:49,600
my father has a black one

387
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:50,840
that looks very similar.

388
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:59,040
All my wife's belongings are here.

389
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:00,480
Feel free to look around.

390
00:19:21,360 --> 00:19:22,200
Look,

391
00:19:22,840 --> 00:19:24,520
