a specialty of Licheng.

392
00:19:24,840 --> 00:19:25,920
It has two sides.

393
00:19:28,360 --> 00:19:29,440
Ms. Lu,

394
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:30,960
you are really knowledgeable.

395
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:33,400
I've been to Licheng.

396
00:19:33,760 --> 00:19:34,680
Even the Empress

397
00:19:34,760 --> 00:19:36,360
uses a double-sided mirror.

398
00:19:36,760 --> 00:19:37,920
Made with quenched bronze

399
00:19:38,360 --> 00:19:39,520
and black powdered tin,

400
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:40,920
and polished with white felt,

401
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:42,240
it shows superb craftsmanship,

402
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:44,560
especially this double-sided design.

403
00:19:45,080 --> 00:19:45,680
Look,

404
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:47,320
press this bronze button,

405
00:19:47,720 --> 00:19:48,640
